sql:
SELECT COUNT(image_id) AS image_count
FROM image_access
WHERE user_id = 0;

SELECT COUNT(image_id) AS high_confidence_images
FROM image_annotations
WHERE confidence_level = 'high';

SELECT image_name, confidence_score
FROM images
ORDER BY confidence_score DESC;

external_knowledge:
- Target images refer to images with a target value of 1 in the images table; 
- Diagnoses and image features include various attributes like diagnosis name, severity, treatment options, width, height, anatomical site, ratio, mean, standard deviation, and feature extraction method; 
- Access details include the number of times images have been accessed, average access duration, and last access date.

sql:
SELECT 
    p.patient_name,
    d.diagnosis_name,
    d.severity,
    d.treatment_options,
    if.width,
    if.height,
    if.anatom_site_general,
    if.ratio,
    if.mean,
    if.std,
    if.mean_norm,
    if.std_norm,
    if.feature_extraction_method,
    if.feature_extraction_date,
    if.confidence_interval,
    COUNT(ia.access_id) AS access_count,
    AVG(ia.access_duration) AS avg_access_duration,
    MAX(ia.access_date) AS last_access_date
FROM 
    images i
INNER JOIN 
    patients p ON i.patient_id = p.patient_id
INNER JOIN 
    diagnoses d ON i.diagnosis = d.diagnosis_name
INNER JOIN 
    image_features if ON i.image_id = if.image_id
LEFT JOIN 
    image_access ia ON i.image_id = ia.image_id
WHERE 
    i.target = 1
GROUP BY 
    p.patient_name, d.diagnosis_name, d.severity, d.treatment_options, if.width, if.height, if.anatom_site_general, if.ratio, if.mean, if.std, if.mean_norm, if.std_norm, if.feature_extraction_method, if.feature_extraction_date, if.confidence_interval
ORDER BY 
    p.patient_name;

external_knowledge:
- "Older than 40" refers to patients with an age greater than 40 years; 
- "High confidence score" refers to a confidence score above 0.85, indicating a high level of certainty in the image diagnosis; 
- "Accessed more than five times" refers to images with an access count greater than 5, indicating frequent access by users.

; Reviewed images refer to images that have been thoroughly examined and validated; 
; Approved consent status means the patient has given permission for their data to be used for research purposes; 
; Average confidence score represents the machine learning model's accuracy in diagnosing the condition.
